   <h2> FUN FACTS </h2>
   <ol>
    <li> Did you know that styrofoam is mostly air? This is why people don't want to 
     make technology to recycle it-they don't think it's cost effective. </li> 
    <li> Did you know that you can't recycle a pizza box? Although it is made out of cardboard,
     the pizza grease on it makes it non-recyclable. Unless your pizza box has never had 
     pizza on it, (or has a protective piece of plastic or something), it is not recyclable, so don't
     make the mistake of recycling it.
     
